Object.Field: ALTER TABLE client_unique_map ADD unique_key NUMBER(20)
CREATE SEQUENCE client_map_seq START WITH 1 INCREMENT BY 1 CACHE 100

CREATE TABLE client_unique_map AS (SELECT NULL client_id,t.prov_id, t.assigned_id FROM <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("PROD7", "D")%>.CLIENT_OVERSIGHT @ <%=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_DSERV_NAME")%> t WHERE t.assigned_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY t.prov_id, t.assigned_id UNION ALL SELECT t.client_id,t.prov_id, t.assigned_id FROM <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("PROD7", "D")%>.CLIENT_OVERSIGHT@ @ <%=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_DSERV_NAME")%> WHERE t.assigned_id is NULL )

INSERT /*+ APPEND */ INTO dim_client_oversight(id,client_id,oversight_prov_id,assigned_id,unique_key) (SELECT co.id,co.client_id,co.prov_id,co.assigned_id,um.unique_key FROM <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("PROD7", "D")%>.client_oversight@bidb01bd_prod7_link co, client_unique_map um WHERE (co.prov_id=um.prov_id) AND (co.assigned_id = um.assigned_id) UNION ALL SELECT co.id,co.client_id,co.prov_id,co.assigned_id,um.unique_key FROM <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("PROD7", "D")%>.client_oversight@bidb01bd_prod7_link co, client_unique_map um WHERE (co.prov_id=um.prov_id) AND (co.client_id = um.client_id) )

UPDATE dim_client_oversight co SET co.oversight_prov_code = (select pv.code from <%=odiRef.getSchemaName("PROD7", "D")%>.PROVIDER @ <%=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_DSERV_NAME")%> pv where pv.id = co.oversight_prov_id)
